    caption: [Amyloplasts filled with starch (dark granules) are stained with iodine in this section of Ranunculus root cells. Starch granules in various tissues range from 1 to 100 (cid:2)m in diameter. c20CarbohydrateBiosynthesisInPlantsAndBacteria.indd Page 801 01/10/12 11:29 AM user-F408 c20CarbohydrateBiosynthesisInPlantsAndBacteria.indd Page 801 01/10/12 11:29 AM user-F408 /Users/user-F408/Desktop /Users/user-F408/Desktop],
